race.description: Wrc Ga Tickets On Sale Now! Open Handicap
race.comment: The four leading chances come out of the same race at the track. SWEET KISSES (4) resumed winning here this grade over 1200m and then led them up and tired in the latter stages over 1200m. She's one 4/6 here at 1400m and has a low gate and handy 2kg claim. She can bounce with the extra fitness. TYCOON BEAU (5) settled too far back in the same contest following a good win at Cairns over this distance. 2x winning rider Wiggins is reunited and he maps for the run of the race. Has winning claims. TAMBO'S JUSTICE (6) will be fitter and flies here second-up and over the trip. Races forward and also deserves plenty of consideration. NORTHERN PRIDE (1) was plainer in the same contest but his win this grade/trip at Mackay prior stacks up.
